    <item>
      <title>据称阿达尼计划为旗舰公司融资 12 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/billionaire-adani-said-to-plan-raising-1-2-billion-for-flagship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的旗舰公司正考虑通过出售股票筹集约 1000 亿卢比（12 亿美元）至 1200 亿卢比，此前他的电力传输部门刚刚完成了另一项融资交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/billionaire-adani-said-to-plan-raising-1-2-billion-for-flagship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:44:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国经济放缓危及中国出口驱动型复苏之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-economy-imperils-china-path-of-exporting-its-way-to-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的出口引擎对于保持中国实现5%左右的增长目标至关重要，但现在，美国需求下滑的迹象正对出口造成威胁，而北京方面也在努力提振自身的消费经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-economy-imperils-china-path-of-exporting-its-way-to-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行鸽派信号削弱进一步加息预期 日元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长内田新一表示，如果金融市场不稳定，政策制定者将不会进一步提高基准利率，随后日元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
